pom.xml
----------
1) dependencies ----> download libraries and attach them to current project
2) plugins ----> defining the goals


Maven Goals
	compile
	run
	test
	package
	install


How to install maven on windows
----------------------------

Pre-requisite: Java/JDK

1) Download pache Maven
	https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi
2) extract zip file, copy the folder in C: Drive.
3) Set Maven path

C:\apache-maven-3.8.1\bin
C:\apache-maven-3.8.1

4) open command prompt then execute below command
	mvn -version


Run the maven project through command prompt
---------
cd C:\Users\admin\myworkspace2\opencart
mvn clean test


